oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Capitol buildings of Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Composite image of the three buildings where capitols were located in Tennessee. In the upper left is a drawing of the Capitol for the State of Franklin, in the upper right is an image of the capitol at Knoxville, and in the middle of the page is an image of the current Tennessee State Capitol in Nashville.
